                                                                                    Sally Seese                                        
                                        
                                        
on behalf of Lori Crawford

 AUBURN, WA                                            





                        For those of you that know Lori she is again fighting Luekemia. She would never set one of these up for herself but chemo drugs and gas for doctors appointments have taken a toll on her families food,bills and frankly life in general at this time. So if you are a good friend or aquiantences or just want to help Lori through this very tough time. Please donate. Lori has always helped when other people were in need and this is when we can pay her back for her friendship and loyalty, thank you from myself and of course Lori's family.  Anything is appreciated.
                    
